What you need to know:  The Elephants, who edged out Zimbabwe Goshawks 36-5 at the Nelson Mandela Bay Stadium, Port Elizabeth, South Africa, are assured of a place in the semi-finalsOdera said they are aiming to end their maiden appearance at Currie Cup on a high before shifting their focus to the Africa qualifier for their 2023 Paris Rugby World CupAfter beating Leopards, Odera said his players now need to prove that it wasn't a fluke by putting up another good performance